<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <%- include('./partials/head.ejs') %>
    <body>

        <div class="app_container">
            <div class="app_header">
                <%- include('./partials/nav.ejs') %>
                <h2 class="app_header-title title is-1">Elementary School Teacher - Springfield Public Schools</h2>
                <h3 class="app_header-subt subtitle">
                    Hello,
                    <br></br>
                    Thank you for submitting your resume! The Springfield Public School district is a network of elementary and middle schools that currently serve over 1,340 students from the surrounding area. Our commitment to holistic child development is paralleled with our commitment to creating a joyful community for families and staff. The primary responsibility of an elementary school teacher is to cultivate a healthy, ambitious learning environment. 
                    <br></br>
                    Our district uses a series of questions for all prospective applicants, that you can answer below. 
                    <br></br>
                    When you're ready, hit "Submit" at the bottom and your answers will be recorded.
                </h3>
            </div>

            <hr></hr>

            <form action="/admin" class="form_application" method="POST">

                <div class="app_body">

                    <div class="app_body-questions">
                        <field class="form" id="question_name">
                            <label class="label">Please provide your first and last name.</label>
                            <div class="control">
                                <input
                                    class="input"
                                    type="text"
                                    placeholder="First and Last Name"
                                    name="_name"
                                />
                            </div>
                        </field>
                    </div>

                    <div class="app_body-questions">
                        <field class="form" id="question-1">
                            <label class="label">A second grader has done well decoding words and improving automaticity when reading out loud. However, the student rarely changes inflections and ignores punctuation, reading almost monotonously. To help the student improve, the teacher should do which of the following?</label>
                            <div class="select">
                                <select name="_a1">
                                    <option></option>
                                    <option class="question_1-op">Have the student partake in repeated readings</option>
                                    <option class="question_1-op" value="ans">Provide the student with text that has phrase boundaries</option>
                                    <option class="question_1-op">Guide the student in encoding activities</option>
                                    <option class="question_1-op">Teach the student about the uses of different punctuation marks</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </field>
                    </div>

                    <div class="app_body-questions">
                        <field class="form" id="question-2">
                            <label class="label">In developing a persuasive presentation, a student has focused on implementing a school-wide recycling program due to the vast amount of trash a school community produces each day. The student will be arguing which of the following?</label>
                            <div class="select">
                                <select name="_a2">
                                    <option></option>
                                    <option class="question_2-op" value="">An assertion of fact</option>
                                    <option class="question_2-op" value="">An assertion of value</option>
                                    <option class="question_2-op" value="ans">An assertion of policy</option>
                                    <option class="question_2-op" value="">An assertion of rhetorical situation</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </field>
                    </div>

                    <div class="app_body-questions">
                        <field class="form" id="question-3">
                            <label class="label">A student is examining a source to use in a research paper. The student does research on the author and source and examines the relevance of the information in relation to the paper's topic. What else must the student do next to determine if the information should be used?</label>
                            <div class="select">
                                <select name="_a3">
                                    <option></option>
                                    <option class="question_3-op" value="ans">Verify the source's information to consider the authenticity of and the amount of possible bias therein</option>
                                    <option class="question_3-op">Examine the complexity of the information</option>
                                    <option class="question_3-op">Determine the readability of the information in relation to the audience</option>
                                <option class="question_3-op">Identify if the source has both opinion and fact</option>

                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </field>
                    </div>

                    <div class="app_body-questions">
                        <field class="form" id="question-4">
                            <label class="label">Which of the following is the most effective way for a first-grade teacher to enhance studentsâ€™ reading proficiency?</label>
                            <div class="select">
                                <select name="_a4">                   
                                    <option></option>
                                    <option class="question_4-op">Encourage oral storytelling in the classroom</option>
                                    <option class="question_4-op" value="ans">Provide effective phonics instruction</option>
                                    <option class="question_4-op">Replace basal texts with real literature</option>
                                    <option class="question_4-op">Have students make daily visits to the school library</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </field>
                    </div>

                    <div class="app_body-questions">
                        <field class="form" id="question_date">
                            <label class="label">Please provide today's date.</label>
                            <div class="control">
                                <input
                                    class="input"
                                    type="text"
                                    placeholder="MM/DD/YYYY"
                                />
                            </div>
                        </field>
                    </div>


                </div> <!-- app_body -->
           
            </form>
            <hr></hr>

            <div class="app_button-container">
                <button class="button is-link">Submit</button>
            </div>
        </div> <!-- app_container -->

    </body>
</html>

